title: No-No Boy - Full Performance (Live on KEXP)
description:
http://KEXP.ORG presents No-No Boy performing live in the KEXP studio and at Panama Hotel in Seattle. Recorded March 19-20, 2022. Presented as part of KEXP's series Immigrants Songs, with support  by The Vilcek Foundation.

Songs:
Imperial Twist
Tell Hanoi I Love Her
Minidoka (performed at Panama Hotel)
Little Saigon (performed at Panama Hotel)
Boat People
Panda Scout (as performed by Little Monk Panda Scout)

Julian Saporiti - Vocals / Guitar
Emilia Halvorsen - Vocals / Drum Machine
Julia McGarrity - Viola / Keys
Kyle Lissman - Bass

Host: Morgan
In-studio Audio Engineer & Mastering: Julian Martlew
Panama Hotel Audio Engineer & Mastering: Kevin Suggs
Cameras: Jim Beckmann, Carlos Cruz & Scott Holpainen
Editors: Jim Beckmann & Carlos Cruz

Special thanks to Panama Hotel in Seattle
